cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for deep reinforcement learning using trust region optimization and Kronecker-factored approximation to the curvature. This work is related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
